{"tid":675796,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"上海食客忙打機　美女代客剝蝦月入過萬","createTime":"2018-05-24T00:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T09:57:29.000Z","uid":81228,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"14e6f71eaeb2b9cd7391531fc832a71ac9d1ad3e","tid":675796,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T00:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2075000/2079135/24JHH003__20180524_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2075000%2F2079135%2F24JHH003__20180524_L.jpg&h=82fbbabb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女生稱她兩天就學會怎麼剝蝦。(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n香噴噴的小龍蝦令人垂涎三尺，但有年輕食客卻會嫌剝蝦費時，阻礙他們邊吃飯，邊打機。上海有餐廳於是推出「剝蝦員」為食客代勞，一名美女大學生兼職剝蝦，就月入過萬。<br />\n<br />\n這間餐廳在上海黃浦區，店長表示，年輕人到來吃飯，很多人還要組隊打王者榮耀，或別的遊戲，而剝小龍蝦其實也是件挺麻煩的事，手會弄髒，所以他就推出一個剝蝦服務，「他們就可以手不用停，依然吃到蝦」；餐廳會加收客人15%服務費，全數歸剝蝦員所有，而要求服務的大部分是男生。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>收15%服務費</strong><br />\n<br />\n據報道，該餐廳現時有2位兼職剝蝦殼員，其中一位是在大學讀時裝設計四年級的女生何南新。何表示，她兩天就學會怎麼剝蝦，「如果努力的話，月入可以有五位數字」。對於有人認為這只是餐廳招攬客人的噱頭，何稱，她靠自己的勞力賺錢吃飯，還有機會遇到各式各樣的人，也不是完全沒有意義。<br />\n<br />\n美女「剝蝦員」的消息傳出後引來熱議，有網民稱餐廳是「男生天堂」，又有人嚷着「在哪裏剝，我也要去，剝個蝦都能月入過萬了，我還上甚麼班&hellip;&hellip;」；有網民則感慨稱「大城市剝蝦都能月入過萬&hellip;&hellip;小縣城的悲哀」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2075000/2079135/24JHH005__20180524_S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2075000%2F2079135%2F24JHH005__20180524_S.jpg&h=a34304e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小龍蝦近年成為紅遍大江南北的美食。（資料圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2075000/2079135/022_01_a_20180524_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2075000%2F2079135%2F022_01_a_20180524_L.jpg&h=53f155ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n編輯︰許可<br />\n美術︰陳超雄<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2079135/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%BF%99%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%20%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%A2%E5%89%9D%E8%9D%A6%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2079135%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25BF%2599%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25A9%259F%2520%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2589%259D%25E8%259D%25A6%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2590%25AC&d=GvMfIaxsAroam1iGpigVBgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=1e8aa394\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2079135/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%BF%99%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%20%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%A2%E5%89%9D%E8%9D%A6%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC</a>"},{"pid":"65ba80f699615178472c640a3f1577f3b021aa3c","tid":675796,"uid":86756,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T00:04:41.000Z","msg":"美女係邊..？"},{"pid":"71f72629e97dd6f73ed9b3af9b15e67a815c3ae9","tid":675796,"uid":1589,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T01:00:02.000Z","msg":"d 小龍蝦好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點擺到入口"},{"pid":"87e670ebb4268345dc28582d0d3a8fca70bb226c","tid":675796,"uid":11962,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"71f72629e97dd6f73ed9b3af9b15e67a815c3ae9","tid":675796,"uid":1589,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T01:00:02.000Z","msg":"d 小龍蝦好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點擺